\begin{Shaded}
\begin{Highlighting}[]
\CommentTok{\# Get only numerical columns}
\NormalTok{w\_sample\_num }\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}}\NormalTok{ w\_sample }\SpecialCharTok{\%\textgreater{}\%} \FunctionTok{select\_if}\NormalTok{(is.numeric)}

\CommentTok{\# Calculate IQR, Q1, Q3, lower and upper bounds for each column separately}
\NormalTok{IQR\_value }\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}} \FunctionTok{apply}\NormalTok{(w\_sample\_num, }\DecValTok{2}\NormalTok{, IQR)}
\NormalTok{Q1 }\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}} \FunctionTok{apply}\NormalTok{(w\_sample\_num, }\DecValTok{2}\NormalTok{, quantile, }\FloatTok{0.25}\NormalTok{)}
\NormalTok{Q3 }\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}} \FunctionTok{apply}\NormalTok{(w\_sample\_num, }\DecValTok{2}\NormalTok{, quantile, }\FloatTok{0.75}\NormalTok{)}
\NormalTok{lower\_bound }\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}}\NormalTok{ Q1 }\SpecialCharTok{{-}} \FloatTok{1.5} \SpecialCharTok{*}\NormalTok{ IQR\_value}
\NormalTok{upper\_bound }\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}}\NormalTok{ Q3 }\SpecialCharTok{+} \FloatTok{1.5} \SpecialCharTok{*}\NormalTok{ IQR\_value}

\CommentTok{\# Find outliers for each column separately}

  \ControlFlowTok{if}\NormalTok{ (}\FunctionTok{length}\NormalTok{(outliers\_IQR) }\SpecialCharTok{\textgreater{}} \DecValTok{0}\NormalTok{) \{}
